mail-notification is a service that allows to see the arrival of new mail on the HOME page of xbmc
 
INSTALLATION:
          Add the ZIP file from the XBMC interface system
          Then configure the various mail servers, up to three
          TAB Server
           My Server: The name that will appear in the HOME screen
           User: login to the mail server
           Password: your password, be careful it will be clear from the file setting.xml
           Server Address: normally in the form pop.monfai.fr
           Port: 110 for POP3, 995 for POP3S (SSL)
           SSL: yes or no
           Type:  for the future support IMAP
          General Tab
           Time: Time in seconds between two mail server connections 
 
After you  need to restart XBMC for the service to be taken into account.
